\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.newschannel5.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WTVF</a>]</li><li>Paul House, who&#x2019;s been on death row for almost 23 years, was sent home today on house arrest. New DNA evidence came to light, causing a judge to grant him a retrial. [<a href=\"http://www.newschannel5.com/global/story.asp?s=8584545\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.newschannel5.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WTVF</a>]</li><li>Metro Council has approved a new zoning bill that will allow rehab services to be on agriculturally-zoned land. A few months ago, the group Teen Challenge sued the city for $650K because they had to close their doors when the measure wasn&#x2019;t passed before. [<a href=\"http://www.nashvillecitypaper.com/news.php?viewStory=61198\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.nashvillecitypaper.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">City Paper</a>]</li><li>An 11 year-old boy accidentally shot a 12 year-old girl in the head this morning in LaVergne. The girl is being held at the Vanderbilt University Medical Center in critical condition. [<a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/global/story.asp?s=8611124\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WKRN</a>]</li></ul><p><em>Photo by <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/cgrantham/2628917225/in/pool-nashvillest\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">cgrantham</a>.</em></p><p>Related posts:<ol><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2010/04/30/bright-not-so-early-feeling-texty-edition/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Bright &amp; (Not So) Early: Feeling Texty Edition\">Bright &amp; (Not So) Early: Feeling Texty Edition</a></li></ol></p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\